sections.heading: to 55-6-110 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1992, ch. 114, § 237C repealed 55-6-101 to 55-6-110 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1961, ch. 96, §§ 6-101 to 6-110, relating to bulk transfers, effective July 1, 1992. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1991 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
